videoDetails.Title: War Thunder tanks guide– Improved aiming in realistic tank battle, tips to get better in War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
Episode 3 is about improved aiming and gives you tips and tricks for tanks on how to get better in War Thunder ground forces realistic tank battles. More tips on how to get better in realistic tank battles will follow soon.

I hope you enjoy this video.
